description	"Ugnaught Engineer

^2Weaponry:
- Blaster Pistol (1)

^6Equipment:
- Portable Sentry Gun
- Portable Forcefield
- Medpac (25HP+)

^8Attributes:
- Fast Hacking

^3Abilities:
- Ammo Supply [Hold Use on Allies]
- Portable Field Medkit [Hold Use to Heal Allies]

The Ugnaughts appeared like dwarf-sized humanoids with some pig-like features, such as a slightly upturned nose and chubby belly. Ugnaughts were industrious and loyal workers and also had a rich oral tradition. They were quite hardy, able to withstand long periods of discomfort, and lived to around two hundred years of age."